Subject: BroMances Through History
Description: What is a 'bromance'? 'Guy Love'? Walk with us through cinema history as we highlight the evolution of the bromance. From Felix & Oscar, Wayne & Garth, through Harold & Kumar, we will highlight through film that it is ok to have a 'hetero-lifemate'.
